{
  "info": {
    "name": "EntreNos — Colección Completa (HU1-HU10)",
    "description": "Colección Postman corregida que cubre todos los criterios de aceptación de backend de HU1 a HU10.\n\n## Flujo recomendado\n1. HU1 — Registrar 2 usuarios\n2. Login admin + crear habilidades faltantes\n3. Configurar catálogos\n4. HU7 — Login usuarios\n5. HU2 — Navegar muro, filtrar, ver detalle, solicitar\n6. HU3 — Aceptar solicitud, confirmar ambas partes, calificar\n7. HU4 — Crear subastas\n8. HU5 — Pujar, retirar, historial\n9. HU6 — Recomendaciones\n10. HU8 — Reportar incidencia, cancelar transacción\n11. HU9 — Logros\n12. HU10 — Podio\n13. Admin — Sanciones\n\n## Setup\n- Borrar `data/*.json` antes de iniciar\n- Iniciar backend con `mvnw spring-boot:run`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "token_admin", "value": "" },
    { "key": "token_user1", "value": "" },
    { "key": "token_user2", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_user1", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_user2", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_admin", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_pub1", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_pub2", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_tx", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_tx2", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_subasta", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_propuesta", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_habilidad_diseno", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_habilidad_fotografia", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_instancia_habilidad_juan", "value": "" },
    { "key": "id_instancia_necesidad_juan", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "HU1 — Registro de Identidad y Catálogo",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1.1 Registrar usuario 1 (Juan)",
          "event": [
            { "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
              "if(pm.response.code === 200 || pm.response.code === 201) {",
              "    var body = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('id_user1', body.id);",
              "    pm.test('Usuario 1 creado con ID', () => pm.expect(body.id).to.not.be.empty);",
              "}"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" } }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"nombre\":\"Juan Pérez\",\"correoElectronico\":\"juan@alameda.com\",\"telefono\":\"+58-412-1112233\",\"descripcionPersonal\":\"Soy carpintero y electricista\",\"contrasena\":\"clave123\"}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/usuarios/registro", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "usuarios", "registro"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.2 Registrar usuario 2 (María)",
          "event": [
            { "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
              "if(pm.response.code === 200 || pm.response.code === 201) {",
              "    var body = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('id_user2', body.id);",
              "    pm.test('Usuario 2 creado', () => pm.expect(body.id).to.not.be.empty);",
              "}"
            ], "type": "text/javascript" } }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\"nombre\":\"María García\",\"correoElectronico\":\"maria@alameda.com\",\"telefono\":\"+58-414-2223344\",\"descripcionPersonal\":\"Soy diseñadora gráfica y fotógrafa\",\"contrasena\":\"clave456\"}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/usuarios/registro", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "usuarios", "registro"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "1.2b Login admin para crear habilidades",
          "event": [
